<node id="&quot;POLICY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A legal agreement that outlines the terms of insurance coverage, including beneficiary designations."&lt;SEP&gt;"A policy contract that, along with application questions, answers, and evidence of insurability, forms the full insurance contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"Policy is the legal document that serves as evidence of the insurance coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"The full insurance contract that includes provisions on premium waivers, total disability, exceptions, and related terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance policy that has reached its conclusion, as indicated by the statement 'This is the end of the policy.'"&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance policy that will be issued, which the applicant must inspect."&lt;SEP&gt;"The main insurance contract that includes all terms, benefits, exclusions, and endorsements."&lt;SEP&gt;"The official document outlining the terms, benefits, exclusions, and conditions of the TD 20-Year Term Life insurance."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy allows for voiding of coverage if information is concealed or misrepresented."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy is referenced as having a numbered identifier and governs beneficiary designations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy is set to end and will not be renewed."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy must be drawn up in English."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy outlines terms including benefit adjustments based on underpayment."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy outlines the requirements for proof of claim."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy remains active as long as premiums are paid on time and does not lapse."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-03736d1fd2c6f92ba7855518c6ef9999&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d797d61d4936328367b970f1b1a2a94b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfd5028f0b43132db8da74961939d00d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c9b2d4d50f1eb65ffb1c24f16aaff10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e336bc3335eae1b8a9a02061f363f289&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8865028ed52b3b23f75c2db4581d310&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e3c19fad0ec74d4024195693875376d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9664b19d2f37c02c2b9b34d8418fd48b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e6240fb2796b537f797e57d0cca4a3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e48b2c7f5c340d231cab1e863dc3229</data>
