<node id="&quot;BENEFICIARY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A beneficiary is a person designated to receive insurance proceeds upon the policyholder's death."&lt;SEP&gt;"A beneficiary is a person designated to receive the insurance benefit upon the insured's death. This can include spouse, child, friend, or any other individual selected."&lt;SEP&gt;"A person or entity designated to receive benefits from a policy, applicable if specified."&lt;SEP&gt;"The beneficiary is the individual or individuals designated to receive the benefit if payable."&lt;SEP&gt;"The beneficiary receives the insurance proceeds as soon as the claim is approved."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual designated to receive the policy benefits. Must be named via the Beneficiary Designation Form."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual(s) designated in writing to receive benefits from the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The person or persons named in writing to receive the benefits under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-03736d1fd2c6f92ba7855518c6ef9999&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c9b2d4d50f1eb65ffb1c24f16aaff10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83a54997deba410d10252790d8246be0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9664b19d2f37c02c2b9b34d8418fd48b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c68826329db981562929b8432a5c1ed2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3987d1322918db88e8961dd954bc3f19</data>
