<node id="&quot;ESTATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"LEGAL ENTITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A legal entity representing the deceased's assets."&lt;SEP&gt;"If no beneficiary is named, the policy benefits are paid to the insured’s estate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Insurance proceeds do not become part of the estate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Proceeds payable to 'Estate' are distributed according to intestacy laws if there is no will."&lt;SEP&gt;"The estate of the insured is involved in claims processes."&lt;SEP&gt;"The estate refers to the legal entity representing the deceased policyholder’s assets and liabilities."&lt;SEP&gt;"The legal entity representing the assets and liabilities of a deceased person."&lt;SEP&gt;"The legal entity representing the assets and liabilities of a deceased person; if no beneficiary is designated, the benefit may be paid to the policy owner's estate."&lt;SEP&gt;"The legal entity representing the deceased person's assets, to which the benefit may be paid if no beneficiary exists."&lt;SEP&gt;"The legal entity that receives the Sum Insured if no beneficiary is named."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8236a16ecbc3d46f2cffaf18c4b6343f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03736d1fd2c6f92ba7855518c6ef9999&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c9b2d4d50f1eb65ffb1c24f16aaff10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6297aea6185daf9585122e54b144c60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8865028ed52b3b23f75c2db4581d310&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9664b19d2f37c02c2b9b34d8418fd48b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c68826329db981562929b8432a5c1ed2</data>
</node>
