<node id="&quot;INSURED PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The Living Benefit is paid directly to the insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual covered by the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose age and sex are recorded in the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy, whose health is not a factor in conversion."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy; if they die while the policy is active, a benefit is paid."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy; the policy provides benefits upon their death."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered by the policy; the trustee gains entitlement only after this person's death."&lt;SEP&gt;"The individual whose life is covered under the insurance policy, for whom premiums are paid until age 65."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual covered by the policy who may become totally disabled and qualify for premium waivers. Their eligibility depends on the duration and cause of disability."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual covered by the policy, whose death triggers potential benefit payment."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person is the individual whose life is covered by the insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person must be alive and is the individual covered by the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured person must be alive for reinstatement to be possible."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8236a16ecbc3d46f2cffaf18c4b6343f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-03736d1fd2c6f92ba7855518c6ef9999&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d797d61d4936328367b970f1b1a2a94b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e336bc3335eae1b8a9a02061f363f289&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8865028ed52b3b23f75c2db4581d310&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e3c19fad0ec74d4024195693875376d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb04334968af2cf23772b1234fa1ff3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b292e542e11e187b7d8150c2a86ba7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e48b2c7f5c340d231cab1e863dc3229</data>
