<node id="&quot;SPOUSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A legally married partner."&lt;SEP&gt;"A married partner eligible for the insurance coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"A married partner who is automatically considered an irrevocable beneficiary in Quebec unless otherwise designated."&lt;SEP&gt;"A spouse designated as a beneficiary is deemed irrevocable unless specified as revocable."&lt;SEP&gt;"A spouse is a person who can be covered under the insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A spouse who can be covered under the insurance policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"In Quebec, a spouse is automatically an irrevocable beneficiary unless designated as revocable."</data>
