<node id="&quot;PREMIUM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"TD determines the right premium based on collected information."&lt;SEP&gt;"The premium is a payment required to maintain the policy, and its non-payment within the grace period leads to lapse."&lt;SEP&gt;"The premium is set and guaranteed for each 20-year term of insurance coverage and will not change during that term, regardless of age or health, as long as payments are made on time and the policy remains active."</data>
